This paper discusses the use of ensemble methods for classification, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other possible categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), as these categories also cover topics related to machine learning and classification.
